          "description": "One time let's date back to 2022 The pharmacist and staff members were friendly and efficient. Medications were delivered in a timely manner. I was pleased with the service. However, within the last five months, I noticed a change in customer service. I think it is under the new management and the service has not been the best. I was told on Saturday that my medication would be delivered on Sunday just to find out the pharmacy is closed on Sunday. Not to mention the medication should have been delivered on Saturday. I am frustrated because I require the medication daily. I could have made other arrangements to pick up the prescription. I would like to believe it was an oversight",
