          "description": "I have been coming to this pharmacy since I was a child. The staff was and still helpful and courteous to all the customers that ask for help.\nI recently had to pick up medication and the pharmacy was closing but there was a clerk who let me in. And I will never forget how I was treated when the pharmacy  was closing. No one was impatient  or irritated with me. To me with that type of customer service given, means so much to the community. In addition I went back to the pharmacy to get my COVID vaccination. And on this day the vibe was no different, the staff was professional and friendly while administering the shots. Thank you Lenox Terrace Pharmacy for being in my life.",
